273
00:19:20,292 --> 00:19:22,502
- Tak ada cara lain?
- Panjat pagar.

274
00:19:25,213 --> 00:19:26,673
Pagar belakang bilik kesihatan.

275
00:19:32,554 --> 00:19:35,140
Panjat! Ha-young, awak boleh lakukan.

276
00:19:39,144 --> 00:19:40,354
