Cepat!

278
00:19:43,940 --> 00:19:46,068
Cikgu Cho datang. Ha-young, cepat!

279
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:48,153
Hei, Dae-sung!

280
00:19:48,236 --> 00:19:49,780
Jangan sentuh Ha-young.

281
