284
00:19:56,411 --> 00:19:57,454
Kamu semua!

285
00:19:57,537 --> 00:19:59,623
Apa kamu semua buat?

286
00:19:59,706 --> 00:20:01,917
Berhenti! Siapa itu?

287
00:20:02,667 --> 00:20:04,378
Ke tepi.

288
00:20:05,087 --> 00:20:07,381
Cikgu, ada anjing!

289
00:20:07,464 --> 00:20:08,632
Tolong buat sesuatu.

290
00:20:08,715 --> 00:20:10,467
Saya takut anjing.

291
00:20:10,550 --> 00:20:11,510
- Tolong.
- Apa?

292
00:20:11,593 --> 00:20:12,677
Anjing? Di mana?

293
00:20:15,847 --> 00:20:17,057
Kamu nak apa?

294
00:20:18,892 --> 00:20:20,685
Pergi sana. Pergi.

295
00:20:20,769 --> 00:20:21,937
Pergi sana.

296
00:20:23,313 --> 00:20:24,648
Budak bertuah!

297
00:20:24,731 --> 00:20:26,525
SEKOLAH TINGGI YUIL

298
00:20:36,785 --> 00:20:37,994
Kenapa?

299
00:20:38,078 --> 00:20:39,162
Seluar awak koyak.

300
00:20:51,633 --> 00:20:52,676
Terima kasih.

301
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:55,720
- Saya…
- Tak buat perkara jahat, bukan?

302
00:20:55,804 --> 00:20:57,180
Tak. Apa?

303
00:20:57,264 --> 00:20:59,015
Betul.

304
00:21:01,309 --> 00:21:02,477
Jangan sampai tertangkap.

305
00:21:18,243 --> 00:21:20,495
- Awak tak nak pakai?
- Tak nak.

306
00:21:20,996 --> 00:21:23,206
Awak juga ahli kelas 1-7.

307
00:21:23,290 --> 00:21:26,293
Kawan-kawan lain setuju untuk pakai.
Awak kena pakai juga.

308
00:21:28,712 --> 00:21:29,880
Heon!

309
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:43,852
Lumba lompat pagar
buat saya sangat gementar.

310
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,203
Puas hati?

311
00:22:04,581 --> 00:22:05,832
Okey.

312
00:22:06,750 --> 00:22:08,376
Dah pakai!

313
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:10,086
Kacaknya.

314
00:22:35,987 --> 00:22:37,364
- "Sayang, jom."
- Saya Heon.

315
00:22:37,447 --> 00:22:39,658
<i>Kenapa susah sangat nak cakap,</i>

316
00:22:39,741 --> 00:22:41,368
<i>"dia teman lelaki dan milik saya"?</i>

317
00:22:41,451 --> 00:22:44,663
<i>- Bolehkah saya cintai awak?</i>
<i>- Bolehkah saya cintai awak?</i>

318
00:22:45,247 --> 00:22:46,623
<i>- Okey?
- Saya fikir dulu.</i>

319
00:22:47,290 --> 00:22:48,833
<i>Kita dah ada pelakon utama.</i>

320
00:22:48,917 --> 00:22:50,502
<i>- Siapa?
- Tak perasankah?</i>

321
00:22:50,585 --> 00:22:51,920
"Tak nampak dia terkejut?"

322
00:22:52,003 --> 00:22:53,880
<i>Terima kasih. Setiap hari menyeronokkan.</i>

323
00:22:53,964 --> 00:22:54,881
<i>Awak memang hebat.</i>

324
00:22:54,965 --> 00:22:56,633
<i>Tidak! Jangan.</i>

325
00:22:56,716 --> 00:22:58,635
<i>- Awak nampak Sol-i?
- Heon.</i>

326
00:22:58,718 --> 00:22:59,886
